### SnapBooth Auth API — VS Code REST Client
### Extension: humao.rest-client
### Jalankan tiap request dengan klik "Send Request" di atas baris ###
###
### Urutan testing yang disarankan:
###   1. Register (sukses)     → simpan token di @token
###   2. Login (sukses)        → verifikasi token baru
###   3. GET /me (sukses)      → pakai token dari login
###   4. Semua kasus gagal
###   5. Logout

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Ganti nilai ini setelah dapat token dari Register atau Login
# @name login
# Setelah request login sukses, VS Code REST Client bisa dipakai:
#   {{login.response.body.data.token}}
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
@token = PASTE_TOKEN_HERE


# ==============================================================================
# 1. REGISTER
# ==============================================================================

### 1a. Register — Sukses (201)
# Harap diubah: gunakan email unik setiap kali test ulang
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Faiza Tri",
  "email": "faiza@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "password_confirmation": "password123"
}

###

### 1b. Register — Email sudah terdaftar (422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Faiza Tri",
  "email": "faiza@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "password_confirmation": "password123"
}

###

### 1c. Register — Password tidak cocok (422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "Faiza Tri",
  "email": "new@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "password_confirmation": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### 1d. Register — Field wajib kosong (422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "password": "short"
}

###

### 1e. Register — Body kosong (422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{}

###


# ==============================================================================
# 2. LOGIN
# ==============================================================================

### 2a. Login — Sukses (200)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "faiza@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 2b. Login — Password salah (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "faiza@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### 2c. Login — Email tidak terdaftar (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "tidakada@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 2d. Login — Format email salah (422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "bukan-email",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 2e. Login — Body kosong (422)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{}

###


# ==============================================================================
# 3. GET /ME  (protected)
# ==============================================================================

### 3a. GET /me — Sukses (200)
# Ganti @token di atas dengan token dari Login/Register
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3b. GET /me — Tanpa token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me

###

### 3c. GET /me — Token salah / kadaluarsa (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer token_palsu_tidak_valid_123

###


# ==============================================================================
# 4. LOGOUT
# ==============================================================================

### 4a. Logout — Sukses, hapus token saat ini (200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4b. Logout — Verifikasi: token sudah tidak berlaku (401)
# Jalankan SETELAH 4a — token yang sama harus ditolak
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4c. Logout — Tanpa token (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout

###


# ==============================================================================
# 5. LOGOUT ALL  (bonus — hapus semua sesi)
# ==============================================================================

### 5a. Login ulang untuk dapat token baru
# @name loginUlang
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "email": "faiza@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### 5b. Logout All — Hapus semua token (200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout-all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5c. Verifikasi: token lama sudah tidak bisa dipakai (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
